      "text": "{user}さん\n恋愛相談があるんですけど、聞いてもらえますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚\nI need some love advice‚ can you listen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛相談？　もちろん、アイドルだからって恋愛しちゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Love advice? Well‚ it’s not like idols aren’t allowed",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いけない訳じゃない。だが、サニピは今大事な時期だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to fall in love. But Sunny Peace is in a crucial period right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛が仕事に悪影響を与えることがあってはいけない\nそれは分かるな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can’t let love negatively impact your work.\nYou understand that‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.2412929376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "真面目な顔で何を言ってるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about with such a serious face?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.1000005722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "恋愛してるのは私じゃありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not the one who’s in love.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.2666672389,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "相談したいのは私のファンの恋愛についてです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What I want to ask is about my fan’s relationship.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.9333339055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ファン？　どういうことだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your fan? What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.2000005722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "全国ツアー中に、私達がファンの願いを叶える\nサプライズ企画をすることは知ってますよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know we’re planning a surprise event\nduring the tour to grant a fan’s wish‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.2333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "それで、私も過去にもらったファンレターから\n叶えたい夢や願いが書いてあるものを探したんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I looked through the fan letters I’ve received\nfor ones that mentioned a dream or wish they wanted to come true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "その中に恋愛相談があったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was there a letter asking you for love advice?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.1333336513,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "はい……恋愛で悩んでるから\n私に恋のアドバイスをしてほしいって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… They’re having trouble with love‚\nso they asked me for some love advice…",
        "id": ""
      },
